Assignment : Write a program which accept file name and on mode and that program
check whether our process can access that file in accepted mode or not.

Description :
We will "open" sys call to open the file.
Accept file name and mode from user and open respective file in that specific mode.
peerror is used for printing the error accordingly.
we will be using access function to chec the access permission for the opened file.
NOTE:
Assuming parameter sequence as follows
1. file name
2. Mode

Accepted mode are as follows :
1. r
2. w
3. x

Will print if the file is accessible in that mode.